textAnnotation.text: every 30 seconds until the burger is prepared (then parallel event moves on)
a human places an order for the robot to carry out automatically
once received the robot starts preparing
note: I left out the question about the size (menu - drink, side dish), as the parallel event only goes on if every edge is done, this keeps the process more compact and easier to read I think
I assume you have to pay after receiving and eating the burger/menu at the cash desk (a person sits there)
